{# Bail Application Template - English | Based on tier2 template corpus #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Bail Application</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7; margin: 40px; color: #222; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #000; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .header h2 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; }
        .court-heading { text-align: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .section { margin: 16px 0; }
        .section-title { font-weight: bold; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 6px 10px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        p { margin: 6px 0; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .parties { text-align: center; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 12px; }
        .versus { font-weight: bold; margin: 6px 0; }
        .grounds-list { margin-left: 24px; }
        .grounds-list li { margin: 6px 0; font-size: 11px; }
        .prayer-box { border: 1px solid #999; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0; background: #fafafa; }
        .signature-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 40px; }
        .sig-block { width: 45%; }
        .sig-line { border-top: 1px solid #000; padding-top: 4px; font-size: 11px; margin-top: 32px; }
        .disclaimer { font-size: 9px; border: 1px solid #999; padding: 8px; background: #fffacd; margin-top: 24px; line-height: 1.5; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>Application for Regular Bail</h1>
    <h2>Under Section 480 of Bharatiya Nagarik Suraksha Sanhita, 2023 (BNSS)<br>
        <span style="font-size:10px; font-weight:normal;">(formerly Section 437 of CrPC, 1973)</span>
    </h2>
</div>

<div class="court-heading">
    In the Court of {{ court_name }}<br>
    {{ court_jurisdiction }}
</div>

<div class="parties">
    <p><strong>Bail Application No.: _______ of {{ year }}</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top:10px;">{{ accused_name }},<br>
    Aged: {{ accused_age }} years, S/o / D/o {{ accused_parent }},<br>
    Residing at: {{ accused_address }}<br>
    <strong>... Applicant/Petitioner</strong></p>
    <p class="versus">VERSUS</p>
    <p>State of {{ state }}<br>
    <strong>... Respondent</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Case Details</div>
    <p><strong>FIR / Case No.:</strong> {{ fir_number }}</p>
    <p><strong>Date of FIR:</strong> {{ fir_date }}</p>
    <p><strong>Police Station:</strong> {{ police_station }}</p>
    <p><strong>Offence(s) Charged:</strong> {{ offence_sections }}</p>
    <p><strong>Date of Arrest:</strong> {{ arrest_date }}</p>
    <p><strong>Date of Current Application:</strong> {{ application_date }}</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Grounds for Bail</div>
    <p>It is most respectfully submitted that:</p>
    <ol class="grounds-list">
        <li>The applicant is a permanent resident of {{ accused_address }} and has strong roots in the community. He/She is not likely to flee or abscond.</li>
        <li>The applicant has been in judicial custody since {{ arrest_date }} and has cooperated fully with the investigation.</li>
        <li>The investigation in the matter is complete / substantially complete and the applicant's continued custody is not required for the purpose of investigation.</li>
        <li>{{ custom_ground_1 }}</li>
        <li>{{ custom_ground_2 }}</li>
        <li>The applicant is the sole breadwinner of his/her family and his/her continued detention is causing undue hardship to his/her dependents.</li>
        <li>The applicant undertakes to comply with all conditions that this Hon'ble Court may impose while granting bail.</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Statement of Facts</div>
    <p style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{ case_facts }}</p>
</div>

<div class="prayer-box">
    <div class="section-title">Prayer</div>
    <p>In view of the foregoing, it is most humbly prayed that this Hon'ble Court may be pleased to:</p>
    <ol class="grounds-list">
        <li>Grant regular bail to the applicant in connection with FIR No. {{ fir_number }} registered at {{ police_station }};</li>
        <li>Impose such conditions as this Hon'ble Court may deem fit and proper;</li>
        <li>Pass such other and further orders as this Hon'ble Court may deem fit and proper in the interest of justice.</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Verification</div>
    <p>I, {{ accused_name }}, the applicant herein, do hereby solemnly affirm and declare that the contents of this application are true and correct to the best of my knowledge and belief.</p>
    <p>Verified at {{ verification_place }} on this {{ application_date }}.</p>
</div>

<div class="signature-row">
    <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="sig-line">
            Advocate for the Applicant<br>
            (Name: _________________________)
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sig-block" style="text-align:right;">
        <div class="sig-line" style="border-top: 1px solid #000;">
            {{ accused_name }}<br>
            (Applicant/Petitioner)
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">
    <strong>⚠ IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER:</strong> This document is generated under the Bharatiya Nagarik Suraksha Sanhita, 2023 (BNSS).
    This is NOT legal advice. Every bail matter is fact-specific and jurisdiction-dependent.
    Please have this application reviewed and filed by a qualified advocate.
    LegalSarthi assumes no liability for the use of this template.
</div>

</body>
</html>
